2166Parittārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca parittārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā—  parittārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca tayo khandhā…pe…  dve khandhā. Paṭisandhikkhaṇe…pe… . (1)
2167Mahaggatārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca mahaggatārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā—  mahaggatārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca tayo khandhā…pe…  dve khandhā. Paṭisandhikkhaṇe…pe… . (1)
2168Appamāṇārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appamāṇārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā—  appamāṇārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca tayo khandhā…pe…  dve khandhā. (1)
